      "writtenOn": "2020-12-07T23:27:44Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I don\u0027t think I understand what\u0027s proposed here.\n\nNor still do I understand why we do anything special ever for alpha-only color types.  We have a consistent model for colors with missing channels, and alpha-only things should just draw as black with alpha.",
